file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  description: '<font size="2" color="red">MIT License</font>'
  title: "Soap-To-Rest"
  contact:
    name: Erlan Lucio
    url: https://github.com/lucioerlan
  version: '1.0'
servers:
- url: https://soap-to-rest.herokuapp.com/api
  variables: {}
paths:
  /consultZip:
    post:
      tags:
      - ROUTES
      summary: JSON TO XML
      operationId: JSONTOXML
      parameters: []
      requestBody:
        description: ''
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/JSONTOXMLREQUEST'
            example:
              cep: '69914366'
        required: true
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
          headers: {}
      deprecated: false
components:
  schemas:
    JSONTOXMLREQUEST:
      title: JSONTOXMLREQUEST
      required:
      - cep
      type: object
      properties:
        cep:
          type: string
      example:
        cep: '69914366'
tags:
- name: ROUTES
  description: ''
